import React from 'react'; const Profile = ({ onNavigate, currentUser, onLogout }) => { const userStats = { totalMeals: 127, avgCalories: 1850, streak: 15, joinDate: currentUser?.createdAt || '2024-01-15' }; return (
{/* Header */}

{currentUser?.name || 'User'}

{currentUser?.email || 'user@bcm.com'}

{/* Stats Cards */}
{userStats.totalMeals}
Total Meals
{userStats.avgCalories}
Avg Calories
{userStats.streak}
Day Streak
{new Date(userStats.joinDate).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'short', year: 'numeric' })}
Member Since
{/* Menu Options */}
Settings
App preferences and goals
{/* Logout Button */}
); }; export default Profile;
